message.raw:
Merging alterations made to run Neo in single-shot sequences
Sequence now always does "Compute" and "Redraw" following acquisition
"Compute" uses shift register to accumulate computations (in case of no data)
"Fit" always called if "auto fit" selected, will fit to raw data frame if computed data not available
